com.misc.common.moplaf.solver

Interface GeneratorTuple

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, GeneratorElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeneratorTupleImpl

    public interface GeneratorTuple
extends GeneratorElement
    A representation of the model object 'Generator Tuple'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Generator As Root
    • Tuple Element
    • Tuple Container
    • Var
    • Cons
    • Code
    • Members
    See Also:
    SolverPackage.getGeneratorTuple()
